channel.title: Most Disgusting Food Ever Ate!
channel.description:
There is this channel on Youtube I go to a fair bit to watch their shows and they show themselves eating a bunch of weird stuff a lot of times and many times puking afterwards.
They recently posted on their twitter asking for more ideas/getting feedback on what the worst food you ever ate before. Figured this might be an interesting topic to compare with people all over the world.
So I ask you Mopar, what is the worst food you have ever eaten? How would you rate it? 1 being ... omg freaking gross * vomit * to 5 being... pretty good actually would eat again!.
Drinks can be posted instead of food as well.
[hr]
Myself... I ate about a ten year old can of Popeye spinach once...yeah it was sick... I give it a definite ONE.

The soda was completely flat, so it was basically watery flavored syrup and IT IS 20 YEARS OLD. That is 20 years of plastic being released from the contained into 20 year old clear syrup. We have no idea of the conditions that soda has been put through. For all we know it could have been put outside in the sun or left in a garage for 20 years in sweltering heat and then refrozen every winter. Anybody else have any stories/disgusting food?[/quote]
